{"tid":1980990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一個月就有6件！東京街頭「橫死」　竟發現武漢肺炎確診","createTime":"2020-04-20T12:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T13:04:27.000Z","uid":35519,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9abc0f534e8d530f55fd941f7b15e0a342ba073d","tid":1980990,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/369/5e4bcd92941e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F369%2F5e4bcd92941e1.jpg&h=ef6c1de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（中央社東京20日綜合外電報導）日本TBS電視台今天報導，在日本東京都自家或路上死亡，被警視廳當成「橫死」案處理，卻在之後接受病毒檢查確診感染中國武漢肺炎，過去一個月內就有6件。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本TBS電視台報導，本月9日清晨4時30分左右，60多歲男性被人發現倒臥在東京都足立區北千住站附近道路上，並在之後死亡。雖然不清楚男性死因，但因為在送醫急救時自述「胸口不舒服」，因此相關人員在男性死亡後進行PCR檢查，結果確診感染。<br />\n<br />\n搜查相關人士表示，從3月20日到本月20日的一個月間，東京都內就發生6起在自家或路上死亡，之後確診感染的案例。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>值得關注的是，這6起案例死者在生前都沒有前往醫療機構看診</ins></strong>，其中也有案例可能是病情驟變。<br />\n<br />\n截至今日下午3時38分為止，日本累積確診人數達1萬0797人，236人因染疫死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">中央通訊社　https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202004200142.aspx\nNewtalk新聞　https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-20/394310</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7dea5bd0c2f8e26e239c56e79e9b1993842e81ee","tid":1980990,"uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"諗起當日武漢　街上面暴斃啲人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20200131/c1_3509349.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.bangkokpost.com%2Fmedia%2Fcontent%2F20200131%2Fc1_3509349.jpg&h=42d86779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xtBDXpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxtBDXpu.jpg&h=f2dcd626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1wNGVa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wNGVa9.jpg&h=e75128fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f51bd93df37d077e262d35dbf4933e070fc49e2c","tid":1980990,"uid":2644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}